  <lyrics>[V1]
 Señor Jesusniy munakuyniyoj.
 Cruzpi wañuspa salvawarqa.
 
[C]
 /Chayrayku takishani: “Munakuwan,”
 Señor Jesusniy, Salvawajniy./
 
[V2]
 Juchaj kamachin noqa kashajtiy,
 Señor Jesuslla salvawarqa.
 
[V3]
 Nina larwayman rinay kashajtin,
 Señor Jesuslla salvawarqa.
 
[V4]
 Kunan sirvisaj Señorllataña,
 Kawsayniytapis Pay man qosaj.
 
